Georg Pleger (born 1967) is public project lead of [http://creativecommons.at Creative Commons Austria] and coordinator of [http://www.stunde.at Tiroler Stunde], a [[Complementary Currency Initiatives|Complementary Currency Initiative]] encouraging the production of [[Commons]].

Member of the free software cooperative [[OS_Alliance|osAlliance]].

My theoretical interests: 
* complementary currency theory and P2P-theory 
* understanding P2P and complementary currencies in an integral framework


